general_info: Tx3 Designs offers personalized technical services in web maintenance, web design & development, social media, computer support services and graphic design. Technical know-how to help your business.  Tx3 Designs will help you find the right solution for your business. If you just need some technical support to help you navigate the tools for your business, we can help get you started and comfortable with the tools that suit you and your business needs the best.   Personalized services are imperative for the small business owners so they can get the most out of the tools available.  - Are you struggling to navigate a do-it-yourself web building tool?  - Is the management of your website and all the various technical marketing tools taking up too much of your time from your business?  - Is it costing more than you feel it should?  Most businesses spend too much money and time on tools that are NOT working for them due to lack of time and lack of support. The importance of setting up your technical presence is NOT because you have to do so BUT to get the full benefit of a 24x7 marketing tool. If your current website and other social media accounts are NOT giving you this - it is time to take a step back and re-evaluate the costs, the effort and the value! Contact Tx3 Designs to help you.
